<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَاهْدُوهُمْ}</span> ... سُوقُوهُمْ سَوْقًا عَنِيفًا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَقِفُوهُمْ}</span> ... احْبِسُوهُمْ قَبْلَ أَنْ يَصِلُوا إِلَى جَهَنَّمَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَنِ الْيَمِينِ}</span> ... مِنْ قِبَلِ الحَقِّ وَالدِّينِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُلْطَانٍ}</span> ... حُجَّةٍ، أَوْ قُوَّةٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طَاغِينَ}</span> ... مُجَاوِزِينَ الحَدَّ فيِ العِصْيَانِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَحَقَّ عَلَيْنَا}</span> ... وَجَبَ عَلَيْنَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُخْلَصِينَ}</span> ... الَّذِينَ أَخْلَصُوا فِي عِبَادَةِ اللهِ؛ فَأَخْلَصَهُمْ، وَاخْتَصَّهُمْ بِرَحْمَتِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِكَاسٍ}</span> ... بِخَمْرٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِن مَّعِينٍ}</span> ... مِنْ أَنْهَارٍ جَارِيَةٍ لَا يَخَافُونَ انْقِطَاعَهَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا فِيهَا غَوْلٌ}</span> ... لَيْسَ فِيهَا مَا يَغْتَالُ عُقُولَهُمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا هُمْ عَنْهَا يُنزَفُونَ}</span> ... لَا يَسْكَرُونَ، وَلَا تَضُرُّ أَبْدَانَهُمْ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٤٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَاصِرَاتُ الطَّرْفِ}</span> ... عَفِيفاتٌ لَا يَنْظُرْنَ إِلَى غَيْرِ أَزْوَاجِهِنَّ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٤٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عِينٌ}</span> ... حِسَانُ الأَعْيُنِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّكْنُونٌ}</span> ... لَمْ تَمَسَّهُ الأَيْدِي.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٥١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَرِينٌ}</span> ... صَاحِبٌ مُلَازِمٌ لِي.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٥٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَمَدِينُونَ}</span> ... لَمَجْزِيُّونَ، وَمُحَاسَبُونَ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٥٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِنْ كِدتَّ}</span> ... إِنَّكَ قَارَبْتَ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>